{meta: title Melva's Wine}
{meta: artist Johnny Cash}
{meta: writer Vincent Matthews}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]Every year about this time
[F]My wife Melva made some [G]wine
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
